  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-01",
      "markerIndex": 0,
      "replayStartSec": 2.41277,
      "replayEndSec": 13.421721,
      "narrationText": "让我们 fork 这个仓库。一条命令克隆了一切，应用、数据库、配置文件，只用了几秒，无论仓库有多大都一样。1 GB、100 GB、1 TB，每次时间相同。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-01.9d0d9c9f.mp3",
      "textHash": "9d0d9c9f52aaa2a9d3c225f4ca158a6bb0eb6319572f531066fd6dd8927b73a5",
      "audioDurationSec": 15.307755,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-01-after.4a7b2ed7.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.440816,
      "afterTextHash": "4a7b2ed76d0a5e3c0da63f4d1510bf627f3e25e344681ba11d9860b0d9f7c2d1"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-02",
      "markerIndex": 1,
      "replayStartSec": 13.421721,
      "replayEndSec": 18.980206,
      "narrationText": "现在两个仓库并排运行。相同的机器，相同的磁盘，两个完全独立的环境。fork 有自己的容器、自己的文件系统和自己的 Docker 守护进程。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-02.800f3518.mp3",
      "textHash": "800f3518aa993600ecb65c3e8441fd128881851d6296a65973021b458a8fb934",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.199184,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-02-after.60bd8ea4.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.989388,
      "afterTextHash": "60bd8ea43805f88b1b009a13af264a1b01c4ec1f57bdeaf352382ca60f3b9767"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-03",
      "markerIndex": 2,
      "replayStartSec": 18.980206,
      "replayEndSec": 26.216902,
      "narrationText": "让我们来证明隔离性。在原始仓库中，我们的标记文件还在原来的位置。fork 的存在没有对父仓库造成任何影响。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-03.7d536765.mp3",
      "textHash": "7d53676523580588ee9ccc9b11cd7f26215799eb92b1e141f24c641b1e363126",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.650612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-03-after.550fd56d.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.004082,
      "afterTextHash": "550fd56dac6830b32ff8e44b9c7eb8e157c5206c4906312715e1aa5aefb2d1ba"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-04",
      "markerIndex": 3,
      "replayStartSec": 26.216902,
      "replayEndSec": 34.456769,
      "narrationText": "现在让我们删除那个文件，但只在 fork 内部删除。在 fork 里它已经消失了，我们做了一个破坏性的操作，它留在了 fork 之内。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-04.b89d7b27.mp3",
      "textHash": "b89d7b2705a62590db6ae67099992a4c926dd026d072a0057e42e65053c005d2",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.650612,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-04-after.e032a061.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 3.709388,
      "afterTextHash": "e032a061d295235fee35bb3f421bdf6515370ec6670a4366cd8e9ef4a1450564"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-05",
      "markerIndex": 4,
      "replayStartSec": 34.456769,
      "replayEndSec": 41.647526,
      "narrationText": "回到原始仓库。标记文件还在这里，完好无损。原始仓库从不知道发生了什么。相同的镜像，独立的 Docker 守护进程，独立的文件系统。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-05.58837c72.mp3",
      "textHash": "58837c72f344392ce4a7182bf187b795d52f361671355608bc613235effafa19",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.389388,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-05-after.8a1d7395.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 2.690612,
      "afterTextHash": "8a1d73955704505d04616f978f7bbe897b51e8a09345643c1273095ac2453779"
    },
    {
      "id": "tutorial-forking-06",
      "markerIndex": 5,
      "replayStartSec": 41.647526,
      "replayEndSec": 51.671921,
      "narrationText": "完成后，直接删除 fork。原始仓库保持原样。Fork、实验、破坏、删除，零风险。",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-06.9bfda771.mp3",
      "textHash": "9bfda7717af602b3487125306f21cb3ccfd017849cdea2171777118942f23147",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.000816,
      "afterAudioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/tutorial-forking-06-after.720c43fb.mp3",
      "afterAudioDurationSec": 4.127347,
      "afterTextHash": "720c43fb080c2175ae0b6adc5a338a851251619dcfd2ca95ab842b90dc81dba1"
    }
  ],
  "narrationAudio": [
    {
      "id": "intro",
      "textHash": "31ffb2efc6eafcd5648112880ef7cfccd9cf4d01bc5426f951b0f0aee40621b1",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/intro.31ffb2ef.mp3",
      "narrationText": "欢迎来到这项杀手级功能！克隆整个生产仓库，无论大小，都不会破坏任何东西。",
      "audioDurationSec": 7.967347
    },
    {
      "id": "fan-out",
      "textHash": "ad0dc99145ee556c8956e4e12b5190cbd38325600441ce6485821d373c53e539",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/fan-out.ad0dc991.mp3",
      "narrationText": "一个父仓库可以扇出任意数量的独立克隆。每一个 fork 都是它自己独立的环境，与原始仓库并排运行。",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.639184
    },
    {
      "id": "link-speed",
      "textHash": "069e536010cf43ad493ca1836082ea42f409fe06a7248edd45384ef4f66827ca",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/link-speed.069e5360.mp3",
      "narrationText": "想象一下分享一个文件夹链接。无论文件夹是小还是巨大，链接都是同样轻量的东西，fork 的工作原理也是如此。",
      "audioDurationSec": 11.389388
    },
    {
      "id": "scale-invariance",
      "textHash": "9ad679d558b91362701fdd7a62c500bc8c7e280c65297f6d4c486a7f37caa91a",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/scale-invariance.9ad679d5.mp3",
      "narrationText": "1 GB、100 GB、1 TB：fork 的表现都一样。仓库大小不会影响这一过程。",
      "audioDurationSec": 9.247347
    },
    {
      "id": "sun-mirrors",
      "textHash": "bfd3122ac7e1b3637e18a1485f506649c9ee87c95f47afc639b5af1bffd8a069",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/sun-mirrors.bfd3122a.mp3",
      "narrationText": "父仓库就像太阳，你的 fork 是接收阳光的镜子。共享的基础保持不变，而你画在镜子上的一切只属于你自己。",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.322449
    },
    {
      "id": "river-photo",
      "textHash": "41aac2b2659ef35144c1f36ce60110db36c5af18dc88d19eca281c4108384c5a",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/river-photo.41aac2b2.mp3",
      "narrationText": "一个 fork 就像在某一瞬间为父仓库拍下的定格照片。父仓库继续如河流般流动，但你的快照保持在拍摄时的样子。",
      "audioDurationSec": 13.479184
    },
    {
      "id": "flat-disk",
      "textHash": "05a19f30025aa34e556d19b94ecd911bfc3cd30a33257107d355a76539c21ee3",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/flat-disk.05a19f30.mp3",
      "narrationText": "一个 100 GB 仓库的五个 fork 在磁盘上加起来仍然只占约 100 GB。你只为每个 fork 中实际改变的字节付费。",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.120816
    },
    {
      "id": "next-tutorial",
      "textHash": "b30cd2d8f1939aacbdc5ae88fa1b92cbbda5b77c4bead764add63c1fe6f64d2e",
      "audioSrc": "/assets/tutorials/audio/zh/tutorial-forking/next-tutorial.b30cd2d8.mp3",
      "narrationText": "fork 故意把密钥留在原地，这正是 “克隆生产环境而不破坏任何东西” 真正安全的原因。我们将在下个教程中正确配置它们！",
      "audioDurationSec": 12.826122
    }
  ]
}
